text: Fisherman's Wharf can refer to: *Fisherman's Wharf, Galveston, Texas *Fisherman's Wharf (Monterey, California), a historic fishing wharf in Monterey, California *Fisherman's Wharf, San Francisco, a tourist destination and still-functioning wharf, in San Francisco, California *Tamsui Fisherman's Wharf, a wharf located in Tamsui (Danshui) District, New Taipei, Taiwan *Kaohsiung Fisherman's Wharf, a wharf located in the city of Kaohsiung, Taiwan *Fisherman's Wharf, Kowloon, Hong Kong, the former name of The Laguna Mall, a shopping mall located in Tai Wan, Hong Kong *Macau Fisherman's Wharf, a theme park located in Macau *Fisherman's Wharf (Stan Rogers' song), a Stan Rogers' song on the Fogarty's Cove album *Fisherman's Wharf (film), a 1939 American drama film
title: Fisherman's Wharf
